512
00:22:06.320 --> 00:22:08.030
Did they over-pluck his eyebrows again?

513
00:22:08.110 --> 00:22:09.320
No. he's in there with your dad.

514
00:22:09.410 --> 00:22:10.780
- My dad?
- He doesn't want the network

515
00:22:10.870 --> 00:22:12.740
